Add try-except blocks to catch FileNotFoundError, PermissionError, and IOError exceptions. Use the following code snippet as a starting point:
```python
try:
    write_file(path, content)
except FileNotFoundError:
    print(f'Error: Path {path} does not exist.')
except PermissionError:
    print(f'Error: Permission denied for path {path}.')
except IOError:
    print(f'Error: An I/O error occurred while writing to file {path}.')
```
